{"type": "article", "id": 5290, "title": "狗狗吊床 Wanmock", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-16T08:00:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233623heAMFzE13D7yLaCm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本 Torafu 建筑设计事务所推出了一款专为狗狗设计的吊床 Wanmock。这款吊床的结构极其精简，选用薄木板制成。用户买回家后，只需将其各零件像拼积木一样拼接起来，不需要借用任何其他的工具和材料。而吊床的床面可以利用家中的旧 T 恤或是旧毛衣，非常便利。此外，每款吊床还会附赠一个木板制成的骨头状玩具，用来吸引狗狗爬上吊床。定价 235 美元（约合人民币 1454 元），<a href=\"http://shop.spoon-tamago.com/products/wanmock-kit\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233621hxSQHzXksIJKE5dF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052336211nWhipbZIOBHUtrF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233622uCekHxz190TIKJ7F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233622SUc8AlHLt9ZJ1a4m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233623a5UTMLqbyJQxnDIi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}